create TABLE DW_ORD (

	PO_CLS VARCHAR(2) COMMENT 'PO구분:C036',
	PO_CLS_NM VARCHAR(1200) COMMENT 'PO구분명:G026',
	MFAC_COMPY_EXPECT VARCHAR(6) COMMENT '예상생산처(PR)',
	MFAC_COMPY_EXPECT_NM VARCHAR(100) COMMENT '예상생산처명(PR)',
	MFAC_COMPY VARCHAR(6) COMMENT '생산처(PO)',
	MFAC_COMPY_NM VARCHAR(100) COMMENT '생산처명(PO)',
	PUB_DT DATE COMMENT '등록일',
	APV_DT DATE COMMENT '결제일',
	MFAC_COST NUMBER(38,0) COMMENT '제조원가',
	MFAC_PROCESSING_COST NUMBER(38,0) COMMENT '순수벤더제조원가 (임가공비), 납품가',
	DSGNR VARCHAR(30) COMMENT '디자이너',
	DSGNR_NM VARCHAR(180) COMMENT '디자이너명',
	DSGNR_TD VARCHAR(30) COMMENT '담당자_TD',
	DSGNR_TD_NM VARCHAR(180) COMMENT '담당자_TD명',
	DSGNR_MTRLS VARCHAR(30) COMMENT '담당자_소재소싱',
	DSGNR_MTRLS_NM VARCHAR(180) COMMENT '담당자_소재소싱명',
	DSGNR_GOODS VARCHAR(30) COMMENT '담당자_제품소싱',
	DSGNR_GOODS_NM VARCHAR(180) COMMENT '담당자_제품소싱명',
	DSGNR_PLAN VARCHAR(30) COMMENT '담당자_기획소싱',
	DSGNR_PLAN_NM VARCHAR(180) COMMENT '담당자_기획소싱명',
	DSGNR_SALE VARCHAR(30) COMMENT '유통MD담당자',
	DSGNR_SALE_NM VARCHAR(180) COMMENT '유통MD담당자명',
	ORIGIN VARCHAR(5) COMMENT '원산지-21F이전:C011,21F이후:C001&val4=SCM',
	ORIGIN_NM VARCHAR(20) COMMENT '원산지명',
	APV_STAT_PR VARCHAR(2) COMMENT '결제상태(PR)',
	REAL_PO_CNTRY VARCHAR(10) COMMENT '실PO국가',
	MIX_RATE_KOR VARCHAR(1300) COMMENT '혼용률',
	MIX_RATE_ENG VARCHAR(1300) COMMENT '혼용률(영어)',
	GROUP_PO_NO VARCHAR(30) COMMENT '그룹PO',
	WH_STOR_ESTM_DT DATE COMMENT '실물류입고예정일(RDD)',
	INCOTERMS VARCHAR(3) COMMENT '인도 조건 (FOB, DDP)',
	STOR_REQ_DT DATE COMMENT '물류입고요청일 (RDD)',
	GOODS_TYPE_CD VARCHAR(3) COMMENT '상/제품구분_코드',
	GOODS_TYPE_NM VARCHAR(54) COMMENT '상/제품구분_명:G025',
	primary key (PRDT_CD, PO_NO)
)COMMENT='제품별 발주'
;

create TABLE DB_SCS_W (
